## 2. Starting Work on a Ticket

### Full Workflow
```
"Start working on CNV-12345"
```

This will:
1. Fetch ticket details (summary, description, acceptance criteria)
2. Show you the requirements
3. Transition ticket to "In Progress" (if applicable)
4. Suggest where to start in the codebase

### Understanding the Ticket

When you start on a ticket, I will:
- Summarize the requirements
- Identify acceptance criteria
- List related tickets (blockers, depends on)
- Suggest relevant code areas to look at
- Identify potential risks or questions

