## 7. Integration with Development

### From Ticket to Code
1. "Start working on CNV-12345"
2. I fetch and analyze the ticket
3. I suggest relevant files and components
4. I help implement the feature
5. I help write tests
6. "Prepare PR for CNV-12345"
7. I help create PR with ticket reference

### Ticket in PR Description
When creating PRs, I will:
- Link to the Jira ticket
- Reference ticket number in title
- Include ticket summary in description
- Follow PR template

