## 8. Tips

### Effective Queries
- Be specific: "Show bugs assigned to me" vs "show issues"
- Use project codes: "CNV-12345" not just "12345"
- Specify status when relevant: "open bugs" vs "all bugs"

### Staying Updated
- Check ticket comments before starting work
- Look at related tickets for context
- Check if ticket was updated since you last looked

### Communication
- Add comments when starting/finishing work
- Document blockers in ticket comments
- Tag relevant people in comments when needed

