## 9. MCP Tool Reference

### Primary Tools Used
| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `jira_search` | Find tickets with JQL |
| `jira_get_issue` | Get ticket details |
| `jira_add_comment` | Add comments |
| `jira_transition_issue` | Change status |
| `jira_add_worklog` | Log time |
| `jira_update_issue` | Update fields |

### Tool Invocation
Tools are called automatically when you make requests. You don't need to specify tool names - just describe what you want in natural language.
